    • CONFIGURE_ACTIVE_ACTIVE_REPLICATION_FOR_CLUSTER

      @Deprecated public static final AdminMessageType CONFIGURE_ACTIVE_ACTIVE_REPLICATION_FOR_CLUSTER
      Deprecated.
      This admin message type is obsolete. Active-active replication should be configured per-store during store creation or via individual store update operations.
      Active-active replication is now enabled by default for all new hybrid stores. Mass configuration of existing stores via admin messages is no longer supported.

    • CONFIGURE_INCREMENTAL_PUSH_FOR_CLUSTER

      @Deprecated public static final AdminMessageType CONFIGURE_INCREMENTAL_PUSH_FOR_CLUSTER
      Deprecated.
      This admin message type is no longer supported and will be ignored if received.
      Incremental push policy configuration has been removed from Venice.
